Vectoroid for Android (Update 12 Jun 2012)

This is a library to use drawings made in vectoroid apps.

It can be used to manipluate and animate the vectors drawn by people for whatever purpose, art, fun, games, presentations, etc.

This software is Dual-Licenced see LICENCE.txt for more information.

DEPENDENCIES:
The GSON librbary is bundled, to install locally use:
mvn install:install-file -Dfile=vectoroid-android/libs/gson-2.1.jar   -DgroupId=com.google.code.gson -DartifactId=gson -Dversion=2.1 -Dpackaging=jar

BUILD :
mvn clean install

Projects

vectoroid-android
The Android APK library
http://www.vectoroid.com

VectoroidExample
The simplest hello world example - loads a drawing from assets
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=co.uk.sentinelweb.vectoroid.example.basic
APK is in target

SuprCardsExploder
This 'explodes' drawings made in SuprCards - the first drawing app. 
It is available on market.
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=co.uk.sentinelweb.example.cards.explode

The demo explodes the hello world drawing.
SuprCardsExploderOpenApp
Housing for SuprCardsExploder
APK is in target

